## Repository structure

```
src/        application code
config/     benchmark configurations
artifacts/  benchmark results and reports
.cache/     rebuildable cache (datasets, models)
docs/       documentation used for the wiki
```

Terminology used in this project is defined in:

```
docs/ubiquitous-language.md
```

